							<Experience
								dates="March 2020 - Present"
								role="VP of Product Design at Tribute"
								body="<ul class='list-disc pl-5'><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Led design and engineering teams while partnering with external agencies to transform Tribute's digital presence. Spearheaded migration from Django to Webflow for marketing, built Vue mini-apps for dynamic features, and created a unified design system with Pegasus.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Drove data-informed decisions through comprehensive analytics setup using Google Tag Manager, Analytics, Amplitude, and PostHog. Executed strategic A/B testing that improved conversion rates up to 50% across key user flows.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Directed end-to-end product development for two native iOS apps, running weekly design sprints and implementing Lean UX methodologies. Leveraged SnapKit and Vimeo APIs while fostering collaborative design processes through Figma.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Managed technical aspects of Boombox acquisition, including codebase refactoring that improved performance by 60%. Resolved 50+ critical issues and implemented optimization strategies that reduced operational costs by 20%.</li><li class='mb-0 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Streamlined operations by consolidating project management tools to ClickUp, resulting in improved team efficiency. Collaborated with marketing to develop and optimize lead generation campaigns and email lifecycle workflows.</li></ul>"
							/>
