								body="<ul class='list-disc pl-5'><li class='mb-0 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Revamped Droplr's digital presence through a custom WordPress multi-site architecture, achieving a 115% boost in organic traffic and near-perfect Google PageSpeed scores (99/85) through meticulous SEO and performance optimization.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Established and implemented comprehensive brand guidelines, creating a unified visual system that streamlined asset usage across all company touchpoints.</li></ul>"
							/>
