								body="<ul class='list-disc pl-5'><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Led product design and development as Senior Manager, guiding teams from initial wireframes through high-fidelity mockups to production code in an Agile environment.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Orchestrated Peterson's complete tech transformation, migrating from legacy .NET to a modern stack including Laravel, Vue.js, and AWS. This 6-month overhaul boosted site performance by 40% while slashing maintenance costs in half.</li><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Designed and shipped a featured mobile app in just 3 months, coordinating with an international team. The app earned a 4.6-star rating and reached 10,000 downloads in its first quarter, landing an App Store feature spot in its launch week.</li><li class='mb-0 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Earned Scrum Master certification (CSM) and implemented Agile practices that streamlined project delivery and team collaboration.</li></ul>"
							/>
