								body="<ul class='list-disc pl-5'><li class='mb-6 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Crafted Inspirato's WordPress blog from concept to launch, significantly boosting user engagement and establishing a stronger digital presence in the luxury travel space.</li><li class='mb-0 opacity-75 text-base leading-relaxed'>Led development for the 'Inspirato with American Express' partnership platform, creating a seamless experience that drove substantial growth in card-member enrollments during the initial quarter.</li></ul>"
							/>
